OL,3,CLucky escape for woman injured by
OL,4,Cmetal pole through windscreen
OL,6,FA Hampshire mum who was injured when a
OL,7,Flarge metal pole crashed through her
OL,8,Fcar windscreen, is calling on drivers
OL,9,Fto take care when tying down loads.
OL,11,FFiona Saunders from Cowplain was
OL,12,Fdriving along Portsdown Hill Road on
OL,13,F18 December when an unsecured pole
OL,14,Fcame off another vehicle and impaled
OL,15,Fher car.
OL,17,FMrs Saunders said: "The next thing
OL,18,Fthere was just noise and pain. I was
OL,19,Fsat in the car, covered in glass with
OL,20,Fthis great big pole sat next to me."
