OL,6,FShe said: "I am so lucky, there's no
OL,7,Fdenying that, I am so lucky."
OL,9,F"A couple more inches the wrong way
OL,10,Fand it would have been a different
OL,11,Fstory. Or if I'd have had a passenger
OL,12,For my children in the car, it doesn't
OL,13,Fbear thinking about."
OL,15,FMrs Saunders says the other driver did
OL,16,Fnot stop, but believes they may not
OL,17,Fhave been aware of what happened.
