OL,6,FShe says she would like them to be
OL,7,Fidentified in order for them to take
OL,8,Ffinancial responsibility and realise
OL,9,Fthe consequences of having an
OL,10,Funsecured load.
OL,12,F"It's not worth taking the risk of not
OL,13,Fchecking, double checking, triple
OL,14,Fchecking that everything is as secure
OL,15,Fas it possibly can be."
OL,17,FFiona has thanked the emergency
OL,18,Fservices, along with the off-duty
OL,19,Fparamedic and patient transport driver
OL,20,Fwho stopped to help her.
