OL,6,FShe said: "I was very very, fortunate.
OL,7,FThe Police arrived really quickly and
OL,8,Fthen the ambulance crew afterwards and
OL,9,FI just couldn't be more thankful for
OL,10,Ftheir hard work and support."
OL,12,FTwo weeks on, she says she is still
OL,13,Fsuffering vivid flashbacks. She hopes
OL,14,Fthat in sharing her story, she will
OL,15,Fhelp prevent it happening to someone
OL,16,Felse.
OL,18,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight
OL,19,FConstabulary has been approached for
OL,20,Fcomment.
